      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Route by Work Type\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: sales, support + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Process 'sales' → Airtable · ②→ Fast-Track 'support' + Alert · ③→ Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)",
