      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Process 'sales' → Airtable\n\nairtable — `upsert` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT",
